11:55.000Z","msg":"因為可以double degree"},{"pid":"99d260c27b6e6aa85d5dc8c2e9e8e4aa3caa67c1","tid":2508982,"uid":367152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"考完個試就衝去quit會唔會急咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇同朋友/屋企人傾下先?"},{"pid":"b64556b4018536ade5c6e9fbe814953de33e1ba3","tid":2508982,"uid":300420,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99d260c27b6e6aa85d5dc8c2e9e8e4aa3caa67c1","tid":2508982,"uid":367152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"考完個試就衝去quit會唔會急咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇同朋友/屋企人傾下先?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"我係考試中途衝出去quit 已經同老竇傾過<br />\n<br />\n我考嗰個試 個course係database management<br />\n但係中間係完全冇database management嘅成份<br />\n<br />\n老實講 <br />\n點樣configure RAID佢唔考<br />\nB-Tree indexing嘅implementation佢唔考<br />\nCollision resistance又唔考<br />\n竟然仲可以叫自己做database management<br />\n<br />\n戇撚鳩鳩含賓周咁喺度畫啲濕鳩ER圖 又relations<br />\n<br />\nER diagram+relation當然係database management嘅一部份內容 但係同正常人注重嘅嘢相差甚遠<br />\n<br />\n當連一個course都可以做標題黨嘅時候（當然只係個人視角嘅問題） 你叫我仲點樣對呢間學校有信心<br />\n<br />\n更進一步 會唔會我之後有嘅一啲睇落去非常合理嘅course其實係好似呢個咁樣呢 <br />\n<br />\n諗到呢度我即刻唔想繼續落去 隨時又俾人呃多一年甚至兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cfb61aa38138b358bdcc01f2a8333fa69dcb3e","tid":2508982,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a600977c5d65d953d78f12f103a2f69c69a7348f","tid":2508982,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"530899fba78a92d5d95e39f83527271cb44887de","tid":2508982,"uid":121245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"講得出要做得到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:31:01.000Z","msg":"屌你 而家搭緊車返去攞表啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"我見linkedin<br />\n好多bba